des:
Simply ask Alexa to turn on/off, change the heat setting or preheat your blanket. 

Connect Alexa to your Sunbeam Bedding S2 app in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Sunbeam Bedding S2" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register a Sunbeam Bedding S2 account in our "Sunbeam Bedding S2" app;
(3). You need to have Sunbeam Bedding S2 device on hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Sunbeam Bedding S2" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Sunbeam Bedding" skill;
(5). Download Amazon ""Alexa"" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with ""Alexa"" app;
(7). Search "Sunbeam Bedding" skill from the ""Alexa"" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Sunbeam Bedding", and you'll be navigated to Sunbeam login page;
(9). Input your Sunbeam account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your Sunbeam Heated Blanket like these:
“Alexa, turn on heated blanket"
“Alexa, turn off heated blanket"
“Alexa, set heated blanket to 5"
“Alexa, set heated blanket to 10"
“Alexa, turn on pre-heat"
